    From Airport framiclad restaurant
    "Airport framiclad restaurant specializes in delicious food featuring fresh ingredients and masterful preparation by the framiclad culinary team. Whether you’re ordering a multi-course meal or grabbing a drink and pizza at the bar, Airport framiclad restaurant’s lively, casual yet upscale atmosphere makes it perfect for dining with friends, family, clients and business associates. Located at sunyani Aiport. We offer a wide array of fresh food – local dishes like fufu, banku ,rice balls and continental dishes like salads, Jollof,fried rice and more. We use the freshest ingredients in preparing our food to provide the best quality and taste. Try our delicious food today!"
